Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart 16

Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart for Violation Per Month by Violation Type

Steps

Violation Per Month by Violation Type, Gender, YOY and Out of State Violation

  1.        Open Visualization Pane
  2.        Select   Line and Stacked Column Chart 
  3.        Drag the visual on to the dashboard
  4.        Drag Description from Traffic Violation table to Shared Axis, Gender Field to Column series, Violation Per Month Measure to Column Values, YOY and %Out of State Measure to Line values 
  5.       Display TOP 5 Violation Type that have high violation per month 




Download the the formatting for the above visual by clicking  the red icon
